BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Killarney] Planned Outage - Arrêt planifié
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260622T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260627T000000
DTSTAMP:20260622T184211Z
UID:drac-incident-1618@status.alliancecan.ca
DESCRIPTION:On Monday to Friday\, June 22-26 \, 2026 Vector's Killarney hi
 gh performance computing grid will be shut down as U of T/SciNet will be p
 erforming data centre-wide maintenance upgrades to the environmental and e
 lectrical systems. A power down of the equipment will begin June 21\, 20:0
 0 ET . During this period users will be unable to login . HPC compute node
 s in all clusters will be shut down and queued jobs will not execute. Runn
 ing jobs will be cancelled. The Scientific Computing team will take advant
 age of these maintenance windows to perform upgrades to address security\,
  performance and add enhancements to the environment.\n\nhttps://status.al
 liancecan.ca/view_incident?incident=1618
URL:https://status.alliancecan.ca/view_incident?incident=1618
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Arbutus] Network Maintenance
DTSTART;TZID=America/Vancouver:20260623T070000
DTEND;TZID=America/Vancouver:20260623T080000
DTSTAMP:20260622T184211Z
UID:drac-incident-1643@status.alliancecan.ca
DESCRIPTION:There will be external network maintenance occurring at the Ar
 butus site on June 23 between 7AM - 8AM Pacific time. This work will invol
 ve about 5 minutes of network impact to external networking during the win
 dow. Network connections inside the cloud will not be impacted\, only ingr
 ess and egress. arrow_back\n\nhttps://status.alliancecan.ca/view_incident?
 incident=1643
URL:https://status.alliancecan.ca/view_incident?incident=1643
END:VEVENT
