BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Vulcan] Planned Outage - Arrêt planifié
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260822T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260823T000000
DTSTAMP:20260630T181035Z
UID:drac-incident-1644@status.alliancecan.ca
DESCRIPTION:Vulcan will be unavailable August 22nd to 24th. During this ti
 me\, you will not be able to log in or run jobs on the cluster. Any jobs t
 hat are running at the time of the outage will be terminated and you will 
 need to re-submit them once the cluster is back online. Power will be shut
  off to the data center which means the file system will not be available 
 and the login nodes will not be accessible. arrow_back\n\nhttps://status.a
 lliancecan.ca/view_incident?incident=1644
URL:https://status.alliancecan.ca/view_incident?incident=1644
END:VEVENT
